 NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/81175/', '', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Sipuleucel-T, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Ropeginterferon alfa-2b, Interferon alfacon-1, Sargramostim, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, More', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole', 1767369485);
